data.text:
Roki Sasaki of Chiba Lotte Marines throws a ball as a starter during a Pacific League baseball game of Nippon Professional Baseball against Orix Buffaloes at Kyocera Dome Osaka in Osaka City, Osaka Prefecture on May 13, 2022. On April 10th, 2022，Sasaki completed the perfect game with a record-tying 19 strikeouts including a record 13 in a row. ( The Yomiuri Shimbun via AP Images )
